SELECT [p].[ProjectId], [p].[AcceptanceDate], [p].[Address], [p].[ContractId], [p].[CreateBy], [p].[CreateTime], [p].[PlanEndDate], [p].[PlanPersonDays], [p].[ProjectManagerId], [p].[ProjectName], [p].[RegionId], [p].[Remarks], [p].[SalesManagerId], [p].[StartDate], [p].[Status], [p].[UpdateBy], [p].[UpdateTime]
